Usage: analyze_paths_by_clock_domain [-help] [-include_edges] [-include_mode]
                                     [-include_views] [-master <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-include_edges     # Considers leading or trailing edge of the clock while
                   # defining categories. (bool, optional)
-include_mode      # Considers constraint mode while defining categories.
                   # (bool, optional)
-include_views     # Considers analysis views while defining categories.
                   # (bool, optional)
-master <string>   # Specifies that the analysis should be performed only for
                   # the specified master category. (string, optional)